Legendary Rogue : Replaces Legendary Sniper COM, buffs fire rate and grants max sniper ammo capacity.
Boosts the following skills : 1) Optics, 2) Kill confirmed, 3) Fearless, 4) Fast hands, 5) Innervate.

Legendary Pistolero : Replaces Legendary Sniper COM, same buffs as a stalker COM,
In addition, boosts velocity and one shot one kill.

Legendary Gunslinger : Replaces Legendary Killer, Jakobs manufacturer, Boosts Jakobs weapon damage and Jakobs critical hit damage,
Boosts the following skills : 1) Optics, 2) Precision, 3) Fast hands, 4) Rising shot, 5) Two fang.

---- Note : If you already have said class mod in your inventory, it will not apply the manufacturer changes.
            In this case you can re-farm one or use gib to update the manufacturer,
            Example : For the Legendary Gunslinger, 1) open Gibbed -> 2) select your save file -> 3) click on your Legendary Killer COM -> 4) manufacturer : GD_Manufacturers.Manufacturers.Hyperion -> replace Hyperion by Jakobs -> 5) save.

Rogue COM : Now boosts Fast Hands, Fearless and Like The Wind instead of Velocity, Two Fang and Like The Wind,

---- Note : Make sure to uncheck UCP's Zer0 Rogue COM changes,
            1) Go to Gear Changes -> 2) Class Mods -> Zer0 -> 3) Uncheck "Rogue COM" category.
